      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "All persons circulating petitions\nfor freeholders' election to revise\nthe city charter are requested to\nreturn the petitions either to the\nchairman or secretary Of the Com\nmission Plan Of Government COM\nmittee not later than noon on next\nMonday, the 9th. Prompt returns\nare important, it being the desire\nOf the committee to file the petit\ntons at the earliest possible date.\nAdoIph Munter, Chairman, Room\nSOB, Peyton block. r. A. Munro,\nsecretary, Room BIS, Hyde block."
    }
